Dear InsightPulseAI Team,

I'm excited to apply for the Business Development Specialist role at InsightPulseAI. Your approach to creating a constellation of AI agents working together with humans aligns perfectly with my vision for the future of business.

My background combines 5+ years in business development with a passion for AI and automation. In my previous role at TechFuture Inc., I helped design and implement AI-driven lead generation systems that increased qualified leads by 47% in just three months.

What excites me most about InsightPulseAI is the opportunity to shape how humans and AI collaborate in a practical business context. I'm particularly interested in working with Edge to co-create agent-enabled consulting offers.

Attached, you'll find my resume and a link to a short Loom video where I explain my approach to human-AI partnership (https://loom.com/example).

I look forward to the possibility of joining your innovative team.

Best regards,
Sarah Chen
LinkedIn: linkedin.com/in/sarahchen-example
Phone: (555) 123-4567
